☀️Summers have started a bit early this year, and so have I with my summer skincare kit😎. We don’t talk much about chafing and how it’s a gender-neutral problematic affair in summers. While I started preparing my kit for summer, this was a must-have✅
There is also a very little awareness about Sunlight aging so let me explain that as well. While we are exposed to harsh sunlight for longer durations, The UV rays not only tans but also speeds up the aging for skin, the term for the same is sunlight aging which leads to sun burn spots and wrinkles. Night is the only time when skin auto-repairs itself and a retinol serum with a squalene base is something that I believe is doing wonders on my skin. 
.
.
@mycosiq , waiting for few more innovative concepts like these✨✨
